editorialNotes.standard: This charming bedtime story will soothe your young child with delightful imagery and a simple but engaging spoken tale. Inside an exquisitely illustrated farmhouse, adorable woodland animals need help turning out the lights to fall asleep. Intuitive controls and fun interactive surprises make Nighty Night a pleasure to explore, and with optional narration, you and your toddler can settle in to be entertained or bring your own imaginations to the wonderful nighttime world.

editorialNotes.tagline: Interact with the power of nature
editorialNotes.standard: Part digital toy and part planetary handbook, The Earth gives kids insight into the workings of our world in a way thats delightfully intuitive and fun. From rockslides to earthquakes to erupting volcanoes, these artful interactive dioramas respond to tapping and swiping with results that are both whimsical and educational. An accompanying guide for parents and teachers delves into the technical science behind all these phenomena, but kids can explore, experiment, and absorb earthly knowledge at their own pace.
